Traxi is one of the workers on the Lovakengj Minecart Network that runs beneath Great Kourend. Players must give her a minecart control scroll, obtained from Miriam, to access her station in Hosidius.

She can easily be travelled to via teleporting to Xeric's Glade by using Xeric's talisman or via teleporting to the Woodcutting Guild via the Skills necklace.
